# Azenquoria Design Guidelines

## App Theme
- Dark theme with primary colors: black, deep blue, and cognac orange
- Use the following color palette:
  - `azenq-dark`: '#0A0F1F' - Primary background
  - `azenq-blue`: '#152642' - Secondary background
  - `azenq-orange`: '#D97C29' - Primary accent
  - `azenq-teal`: '#4FC1B9' - Secondary accent
  - `azenq-text`: '#E0E0E0' - Text color
  - `azenq-card`: '#1A2238' - Card background
  - `azenq-purple`: '#9B5DE5' - Tertiary accent
  - `azenq-pink`: '#F15BB5' - Accent color
  - `azenq-yellow`: '#FEE440' - Accent color

## UI Components
- Cards should have rounded corners (20px radius)
- Use gradient backgrounds for accent elements
- Implement subtle animations for interactive elements
- Ensure high contrast between text and backgrounds

## Typography
- Use system fonts (no external fonts)
- Clear text hierarchy with appropriate font weights
- Ensure readability on dark backgrounds

## Icons
- Use colorful icons in settings and feature screens
- Icons should be simple and recognizable
 